---
/**
 * Contact FAQ Component
 *
 * Displays frequently asked questions about our services
 * and contact process in an accessible format.
 */
import Card from '../core/Card.astro';
---

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="py-24 bg-background">
  <div class="container max-w-4xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-4">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-muted">Quick answers to common questions</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <Card variant="default" size="default">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-3">How long does a typical project take?</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Project timelines vary based on complexity and scope. Simple websites typically take 2-4
          weeks, while complex web applications or AI integrations can take 8-16 weeks. We'll
          provide a detailed timeline during our initial consultation.
        </p>
      </Card>

      <Card variant="default" size="default">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-3">What's included in your web development services?</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Our web development services include responsive design, performance optimization, SEO
          implementation, accessibility compliance, content management systems, and ongoing
          maintenance support. We use modern technologies like Astro, React, and TypeScript.
        </p>
      </Card>

      <Card variant="default" size="default">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-3">Do you offer ongoing support and maintenance?</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Yes, we provide comprehensive support and maintenance packages. This includes security
          updates, performance monitoring, content updates, bug fixes, and feature enhancements to
          keep your website running smoothly.
        </p>
      </Card>

      <Card variant="default" size="default">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-3">Can you work with our existing team?</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Absolutely! We're experienced in collaborating with in-house teams, other agencies, and
          stakeholders. We can integrate seamlessly into your existing workflow and communication
          processes.
        </p>
      </Card>

      <Card variant="default" size="default">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-3">What makes your AI integration services unique?</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          We focus on practical AI implementations that solve real business problems. Our approach
          includes custom AI model development, API integrations, natural language processing, and
          computer vision solutions tailored to your specific needs.
        </p>
      </Card>

      <Card variant="default" size="default">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-3">How do you ensure project quality and timelines?</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          We use agile development methodologies with regular check-ins, milestone reviews, and
          transparent communication. Our quality assurance process includes code reviews,
          automated testing, performance audits, and accessibility compliance checks.
        </p>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
